Class Interval

java.lang.Object
sbw.architecture.bus.protocol.Interval
All Implemented Interfaces:
Cloneable
public class Interval extends Object implements Cloneable
Defines a timing interval for how a service request will be processed.

    • update

      public boolean update()
      Updates this interval. A Interval.E_IntervalType.DEFINITE interval returns its Time.decrement() result; an Interval.E_IntervalType.INDEFINITE never expires; a Interval.E_IntervalType.ONESHOT interval always expires.
      Returns:
